'''Laser-reflective armor''' was a type of [[Armor/Legends|armor]] that was designed to deflect [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] bolts. The [[SD-9 battle droid|SD-9]] [[Battle droid/Legends|battle droid]] was equipped with laser-reflective armor,<ref name="EGTD">''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]''</ref> as was the [[Assassin droid/Legends|assassin droid]] and [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]], [[IG-88B/Legends|IG-88]].

